movie.title: End of Watch
movie.plot: Two young officers are marked for death after confiscating a small cache of money and firearms from the members of a notorious cartel during a routine traffic stop.

events.title: Cops Brian Taylor and Mike Zavala encounter the Bloods while out on patrol
Taylor and Zavala save three children from a house fire
Taylor and Zavala are ambushed, and both are shot
